entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You recovered some data, but not enough. You will need the to tackle the administrative heads and break into their terminals.
entries.journal_entry_description: Find out what kind of place is receiving smuggled chemicals, tranquilizers, and animal feed.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: A datapad on that shipment had a drop location.
entries.task01_comm_message_text: I'm scanning this building's records but nothing is coming up. This can't be good. Find out as much as you can about it.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Lt. Joth sent you a message: I'm scanning this building's records but nothing is coming up. This can't be good. Find out as much as you can about it.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Security on the first floor will have the passwords needed to break into the terminals. Kill them before they kill you and take the passwords.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: You got a general administrative passcode from security. Quickly, before more security is called, get as much information as you can from the terminals.
entries.task03_journal_entry_title: Retrieve Data from the Administrative Terminals
entries.task04_comm_message_text: Good work. Processing this information shows that this may be some kind of lab, but large chunks of data are missing. I need you to extract information from the leaders' computers, by any means necessary.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Lt. Joth sent you a message: Good work. Processing this information shows that this may be some kind of lab, but large chunks of data are missing. I need you to extract information from the leaders' computers, by any means necessary.
